	$LF
]div
[h4 id=MoviesWithShortestDescriptions 
	" Movies with shortest descriptions
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	(MovieStatistics|comp=desclen|fields=desclen=Bytes,num_lines=Lines|need=desclen)
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=MoviesWithLongestDescriptionsInSubmissionEntry 
	" Movies with longest descriptions in submission entry
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"(Note: This table does not include line counts due to technical reasons.)
	$LF
	(MovieStatistics|comp=-udesclen|fields=udesclen=Bytes|need=udesclen)
	$LF
]div
?IF 0
	[div class=p 
		"The line count is included in the site_text database table, but not all submissions have an entry in that table. (Those submitted by NesVideoAgent don't have.) If I include it in the database query, it'll completely drop the movies
		$LF
		"that don't have a site_text entry from this statistics page.
	]div
?ENDIF 0
$LF
[h3 id=RatingData 
	" Rating data
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Note: Only movies with at least 5 votes are listed.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=HighestAverageRating 
	" Highest average rating
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	(MovieStatistics|comp=-averageRating|fields=averageRating=Average rating,numberOfVotes=# votes|minvotes=5)
	$LF
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=(More)|href=/MovieStatistics/HighestAverageRating)
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=LowestAverageRating 
	" Lowest average rating
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	(MovieStatistics|comp=averageRating|fields=averageRating=Average rating,numberOfVotes=# votes|minvotes=5)
	$LF
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=(More)|href=/MovieStatistics/LowestAverageRating)
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=MostRatedMovies 
	" Most rated movies
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	(MovieStatistics|comp=-numberOfVotes|fields=numberOfVotes=Number of votes|minvotes=5)
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=LowestNumberOfRatings 
	" Lowest number of ratings
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"(Note: Only movies published over 2 weeks ago are included in this list.)
	$LF
	(MovieStatistics|comp=numberOfVotes|fields=numberOfVotes=Number of votes|minage=14)
	$LF
